'''社会主义国家的经济计算'''（Economic Calculation in the Socialist Commonwealth）是[[奧地利經濟學派|奧地利經濟學派]]学家[[路德維希·馮·米塞斯|路德維希·馮·米塞斯]]的一篇論文。該論文對[[計劃經濟|計劃經濟]]中的[[经济计算问题|经济计算问题]]的批判，引发了长达數十年的[[社会主义计算争论|社会主义计算争论]]<ref>{{cite book|last=Hacohen|first=Malachi Haim|year=2002|title=Karl Popper – The Formative Years, 1902-1945: Politics and Philosophy in Interwar Vienna|edition=reprint|publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]]|isbn=978-0-521-89055-7|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3VtHcYGp2pIC&pg=PA477|page=477|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2011-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628203143/http://books.google.com/books?id=3VtHcYGp2pIC&pg=PA477|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://mises.org/library/economic-calculation-socialist-commonwealth|title=Economic Calculation in the Socialist Commonwealth|publisher=Mises Institute|accessdate=27 April 2010|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913030435/https://mises.org/sites/default/files/Economic%20Calculation%20in%20the%20Socialist%20Commonwealth_Vol_2_3.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該論文內容主要來源自1919年米塞斯為駁斥[[奧圖·紐拉特|奧圖·紐拉特]]的觀點而发表的演讲，[[奧圖·紐拉特|奧圖·紐拉特]]在其著作中曾試圖證明中央计划的可行性<ref name="Huerta de Soto">{{cite book|last=Huerta de Soto|first=Jesús|year=2010|title=Socialism, Economic Calculation and Entrepreneurship|publisher=Edward Elgar Publishing|isbn=978-1-84980-065-5|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OHcxcMHlXdgC&pg=PA103|pages=103–104|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2011-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628193629/http://books.google.com/books?id=OHcxcMHlXdgC&pg=PA103|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

